          {
            "body": "Sometimes, the gums cover more of the teeth than people realize. A gum lift can change that, making the smile look more balanced. It’s a minor procedure with a big visual difference.\n\nOur blog talks about the top reasons patients choose a gum lift, what recovery feels like, and how our team keeps the process comfortable.",
            "image": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc/AF1QipPe_o4dma8R7MHADddbuLWmhz14-sXvuL0gm_sy=h400-no",
